    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/footer.css">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>About | DOAXVV API</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <h1>ABOUT</h1>
    <main>
        <u><h2>What is this?</h2></u>
        <p>This is a REST API for the Japanese game developed by TEAM NINJA, Dead Or Alive Xtreme Venus Vacation (DOAXVV). This API only provides information about the girls, from the basics to the most characteristic of each one. It contains visual material such as images that are used as resources for the game and videos such as the character trailers.</p>
        <br>
        <u><h2>Why did you build this?</h2></u>
        <p>The idea of ​creating an API like the others that exist based on video games or movies came to my mind. And since there wasn't one for my favorite game, I took the initiative to create it myself.</p>
        <br>
        <u><h2>Who are you?</h2></u>
        <p>I am a guy learning programming and web development with the purpose of improving in this area and with the possibility of getting a job in this environment.</p>
        <br>
        <u><h2>Technical stuff?</h2></u>
        <p>I have developed this site with my basic and intermediate knowledge of HTML, CSS JS, BOOTSTRAP, some logic, etc. And a little help with ChatGPT.</p>
        <br>
        <u><h2>Copyright?</h2></u>
        <p>I'm not trying to claim any of the game's images or videos, but I respect the rights of the creators. That's why I owe credit to KOEI TECMO & TEAM NINJA.</p>
        <br>
        <u><h2>Does this amazing game catch your attention?</h2></u>
        <p>After seeing all the content about the game, I encourage you to visit its official website to download the game.</p>
        <div class="cover">
            <img src="/cover.jpg" alt="DOAXVV">
            <a id="access1" href="https://doax-venusvacation.jp/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-success" title="Official Site">
                <i class="bx bx-world"></i>
            </a>
            <a id="access2" href="https://steamdb.info/app/958260/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" title="Steam Data">
                <i class="bx bxl-steam"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>